#

Beet and Cabbage Soup

60 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegangluten-freelow-calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

main

Tags:

souphealthyvegetarian

Description

A vibrant and healthy soup loaded with earthy beets and crunchy cabbage, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 medium, peeled and diced
  • cabbage: 1/2 small head, shredded
  • carrot: 1 large, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dill (fresh or dried): 1 tablespoon
